      Normalize the Tiling contained in the Experiment
      Run one thread for each bioCondition
      The number of thread is limited by the number of processor

      It runs DNA reference normalization (Hubert et al.), it can uses also an additional reference data for normalization (indicates by boolean normalization).

      static void TranscriptomesCreation.varianceNormalization​(Experiment exp)
      Run some scripts to analyse the statistics of the transcriptomics data and performed VarianceNormalization:
      It will reduce the total variance of each data to 1
      For each column of the ExpressionMatrix, multiply each value by: Math.sqr(1/var(x))
      So final variance of each column is equal to zero
